Gospel singer Mr Seed claims a fellow artiste is working towards his downfall. In a recent post on Instagram, Seed said the person keeps tampering with his projects. "I am a creative who has always worked hard to give my fans the best," he said. "Every project I release has always been special, and together with my team, we have always wished to do it the right way." The singer went on to lament on how some people are trying to bring him and his projects down. "It has come to my attention that someone is working tirelessly to see my work not getting the rightful reception it deserves," he said. Adding, "It won't stop me from being the best as I have always had my fans."